    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ctenobrycon oliverai, paratype, LBP 3061, 50.7 mm SL, premaxillary, maxillary and dentary; left side, lateral view (maxillary and dentary) or frontal view (premaxillary). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
