<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199706>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Map of northern South America indicating the known geographic distribution of Ctenobrycon oliverai n. sp.. Map by M. J. Weitzman." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199707>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Scatter diagram of scores of specimens on first and second axis of Size-free Canonical Variate Analysis of Ctenobrycon oliverai (red crosses), C. alleni (green Diamonds), C. spilurus-hauxwellianus (blue squares) and Psellogrammus kennedyi (violet circles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199707/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199708>
